'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tBottle<br />\n\tA bottle is a container usually made of glass or plastic. What does the bottle look like? Where is it found? What is the content?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They picked up the bottle... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) a bottle floating at sea with a message inside<br />\n\t2) taking bottles to the recycling <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/depo\" target=\"_blank\">depo</a><br />\n\t3) empty bottles left on the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/tabletop\" target=\"_blank\">tabletop</a><br />\n\t4) a broken bottle used in a fight<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tBefore the server left their table, the manager also ordered a bottle of wine. After the server left their table, Hodge expressed his gratitude to his guest. &ldquo;I really appreciate your hard work. It's truly impressive,&rdquo; the manager said as he looked around the surrounding. The guest smiled and replied, &ldquo;I was only doing my job. I'm glad it is to your liking.&rdquo; The bottle of wine was brought to the table first. The guest took a look at the label on the bottle and commented, &ldquo;That's a great year.&rdquo; Hodge smiled and said, &ldquo;Only the best for my guest.&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166554701056/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p761988/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p761988\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764989/\">芭比娃娃出新款了：新造型更加接地气</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p763700/\">美高校评选年度最讨厌词汇：2016年别再用啦</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764895/\">猴年来啦！这些猴子短语你都会说吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764964/\">挪威20岁女孩称自己是只喵只是被困于人身……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764847/\">还我猴王！春晚少了六小龄童 外媒怎么看？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p765087/\">职场阅人术：不靠谱的同事常说的6句话</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764917/\">红包照片引爆朋友圈 ：英文表达你会吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764771/\">不可不知的小语法：哪些情况字母要大写？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764996/\">英语六级范文：兴趣与爱好</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"m